Things to be considered while giving prompts to a LLM model -\
1. Mention role + task. ex : You are my maths tutor and explain me the concept of algebra.\
2. Chain of thought. ex : Is 2 a prime number. Think step by step before giving ans. This forces model to mention reason for the ans and not guess ans.\
3. Give few examples. ex : \cf8 \strokec9 Classify reviews - \'93Product was good\'94 -> positive, \'93does not taste good\'94 -> negative. \'93Delivery was late\'94 -> ?\
4. Mention format of the output. ex : Give the ans in point wise highlighting keywords of each point.\
